bilingual.source: For this reason the space between the walls is reserved exclusively for authorized personnel.
bilingual.target: 为了空间的理由,两墙之间是为主办单位的全体人员专门预留的.

bilingual.source: A special blood bank unit was formed from personnel of the 406th Medical General Laboratory to operate a blood bank there.
bilingual.target: 第406医学综合实验室的全体人员成立了一个特殊的血库单位管理那里的血库。
所有的人员都必须参加培训。
公司雇佣了更多的研发人员。

bilingual.source: This company has a high turnover of personnel.
bilingual.target: 这家公司的人员流动率很高。

bilingual.source: We need more resources for personnel training.
bilingual.target: 我们需要更多的资源来培养人才。

bilingual.source: Only authorized personnel can access this area.
bilingual.target: 只有授权人员才能进入这个区域。

bilingual.source: Only authorized personnel can access the vault.
bilingual.target: 只有授权人员才能进入保险库。
只有授权人员才被允许进入后台。

yingyinNormal.en: Additional CDC personnel are on the scene in Dallas and Cleveland.
yingyinNormal.zh: 其他的疾控中心人员就在达拉斯和克利夫兰的现场。

yingyinNormal.en: It's manned by both military and civilian personnel from District 2.
yingyinNormal.zh: 由第二区的军事和非军事人员共同操作。

yingyinNormal.en: He's right. Take out all legitimate personnel. Anyone that remains is a terrorist.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他说得对，调走所有的合法公务人员，剩下的就都是那些恐怖分子了。

yingyinNormal.en: I think I just shipped 3,000 bras to personnel. Oh honey, I gotta go. Mark, I need you. Okay, bye-bye.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我刚把三千副胸罩送到人事部去了，我要挂电话了，马克，我需要你。好，再见。

yingyinNormal.en: So we need to close the E.R.? We're dangerously low on meds. Personnel can't make it in due to the flooding.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以需要关闭急诊吗？药物严重不足，因为洪水，其他医生没法赶来。

yingyinNormal.en: And as our civilian and military personnel serve in the region, their safety and health will remain a top priority.
yingyinNormal.zh: 有我们在这一地区的平民和军事人员，他们的安全和健康将仍然是最优先的事情。

yingyinNormal.en: In New York City, medical personnel moved quickly to isolate and care for the patient there a doctor who recently returned from West Africa.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在纽约，医疗人员迅速采取行动隔离并照料着在那里的患者，一名最近从西非回来的医生。

yingyinNormal.en: From the United Kingdom and Germany to France and Senegal, other nations are stepping up their efforts, too, sending money, supplies, and personnel.
yingyinNormal.zh: 从英国，德国到法国，塞内加尔其他国家也在全力以赴进行着他们的努力，提供资金，提供物资，派出人员。

yingyinNormal.en: I took those actions this week. We're providing more resources at the border to help law enforcement personnel stop illegal crossings and send home those who do cross over.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我本周实施了这些措施，我们正在给予边境上的执法人员更多的资源，阻止非法越境并将已经越境人员进行遣返。

examination_example.sentence: There's no change to collective bargaining at the USPS, a major omission considering that <highlight>personnel</highlight> accounts for 80 percent of the agency's costs.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 美国邮局的集体谈判没有变化，考虑到劳工成本占该机构成本的80%，这是一个重大遗漏。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2015-2022年全国卷高考试卷，包括阅读、完形、单选、填空、听力、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。
